data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Classy and chic, woo your special someone with this stunning preserved rose arrangement. 'Bouquet of a Lifetime' embodies your heartfelt dedication & lifelong affection, only to be given to the worthy one.

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: Exquisite and everlasting. Our delicate 'Beauty And The Beast' preserved rose is for the one and only in your life. Express your undying love with this timeless ornament that will remind them of your affection.

data.name: description5.Text
data.value: The Sweetheart Bouquet impresses with lush red roses, fine baby breath and white lilies. Sure to please that someone special this combination of premium flowers comes with lavish wrapping and a nice ribbon.
